    {
        "user": "UD4Q9LT52",
        "type": "message",
        "ts": "1779133410.536919",
        "client_msg_id": "914fa163-5b9b-4788-a130-759530ce3a33",
        "text": "Not sure why we wouldn't want to discuss the ideas of a prominent technologist like Elon here. I know a lot of people disagree with his politics, but it's hard to discuss technology without mentioning him. What Elon says in that clip does seem to be a likely outcome if you take the bitter lesson to its conclusion. As for consumerism if Elons optimistic predictions come to pass we will probably think of a lot of goods similarly to how we think of air today. The bigger question I think is how it will affect producers. If we hit post-scarcity will some of us still need to find a purpose, and what will it be?",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_profile": {
