                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_quote",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "If we hit post-scarcity"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "We won't. That's the other problem with people like Elon Musk (in addition to being a bad person): hubris. If you listen to anyone who has made a serious effort to understand stocks and flows of resources in our universe, you will find out that this dream of post-scarcity will never come true, unless there are very serious and resource-relevant holes in our understanding of physics.\nWell, there is one exception: a drastic reduction of the human population of this planet. The survivors can enjoy post-scarcity for a while. At a poverty level, but still."
                            }
